  "content": "<img alt=\"Weekly Update 507\" src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/fb/33/fb3391dc-723d-4e74-b95a-d641b5feb38e/content/images/2026/06/Splash-Template@1x_1.jpg\" /><p>1,000 breaches is one hell of a milestone. It&apos;s not just the process of getting data, verifying it, loading it, sending notifications etc, it&apos;s all the other stuff that goes into keeping the whole thing afloat. Legal docs. Trademarks. Accounting. Agreements. The most mind-numbingly boring stuff you can imagine happening in the background so that the stuff you see in the foreground can all work. And then there are those &quot;other things&quot; I had to deal with along the way, but more of that in this week&apos;s video. Thanks to everyone who has stuck around to see this thing reach such a milestone &#x1f64f;</p>\n<!--kg-card-begin: html-->\n<div><div style=\"width: 170px; display: inline-block; margin-right: 3px;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/au/podcast/troy-hunts-weekly-update-podcast/id1176454699?ref=troy-hunt\"><img alt=\"Weekly Update 507\" src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/fb/33/fb3391dc-723d-4e74-b95a-d641b5feb38e/content/images/2018/05/Listen-on-Apple-Podcasts.svg\" /></a></div><div style=\"width: 175px; display: inline-block; margin-right: 3px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL7LAAxaabizMAXnJe0s3xjQ30q12EVmjt&amp;ref=troyhunt.com\"><img alt=\"Weekly Update 507\" src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/fb/33/fb3391dc-723d-4e74-b95a-d641b5feb38e/content/images/2024/09/Watch-and-Listen-on-YouTube.svg\" /></a></div><div style=\"width: 118px; display: inline-block; margin-right: 3px;\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/7jMtKFohdrw6qmz8AkLqit?ref=troy-hunt\"><img alt=\"Weekly Update 507\" class=\"kg-image\" src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/fb/33/fb3391dc-723d-4e74-b95a-d641b5feb38e/content/images/2019/10/spotify.svg\" /></a></div><div style=\"width: 120px; display: inline-block;\"><a href=\"https://omny.fm/shows/troy-hunt-weekly-update/playlists/podcast.rss?ref=troy-hunt\"><img alt=\"Weekly Update 507\" src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/fb/33/fb3391dc-723d-4e74-b95a-d641b5feb38e/content/images/2018/07/Download-via-RSS.svg\" /></a></div></div>\n<!--kg-card-end: html-->"
